# Configuration for static-analysis MCP server
# Uncomment and modify the ENABLED_TOOLS to selectively enable specific tools
# If not specified or empty, all tools are enabled by default

# Example: Enable only specific tools
ENABLED_TOOLS=get_file_tree

# Example: Enable all tools (default behavior when commented out)
# ENABLED_TOOLS=

# Available tools:
# - analyze_file: Analyze TypeScript files for symbols, imports, and exports
# - analyze_symbol: Get detailed symbol analysis
# - find_references: Find all references to a symbol
# - get_compilation_errors: Get TypeScript compilation errors
# - get_file_tree: Generate file tree with analysis